By default, `.on( events, handler )` does not work for dynamically created elements. 

Base on [this question and answer][1], you can use `$(PARENT SELECTOR).on( events, SELECTOR, handler)` to solve the problem. In your code, it can be `$(&quot;.col&quot;).on(&quot;click&quot;, &quot;.gif-button&quot;, function() { ... });`.

Here is the complete code

